ame) {\n        if (resourceName.equals(name)) {\n            requested = true;\n            return new ByteArrayInputStream(resourceContent.getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8));\n        }\n        return null;\n    }\n\n    boolean wasRequested() {\n        return requested;\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777423821392}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_E8UirruCibA0eueoeePL3Lai|fc_0fb885f13e87b0c80169f155cd051081a1a2926668871cdbe3", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage xerces.xmlParserAPIs;\n\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\n\npublic class XmlParserAPIsTest {\n    @Test\n    public void test() throws Exception {\n        System.out.println(\"This is just a placeholder, implement your test\");\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777423821392}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_oVjG65XUs0lxuVqUYPTWPLxN|fc_0fb885f13e87b0c80169f155cd051c81a19fc5d3255d8100df", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\nplugins {\n    id \"org.graalvm.internal.tck\"\n}\n\nString libraryVersion = tck.testedLibraryVersion.get()\n\ndependencies {\n    testImplementation \"xerces:xmlParserAPIs:$libraryVersion\"\n    testImplementation 'org.assertj:assertj-core:3.22.0'\n}\n\nProvider<Directory> javaXmlPatchDir = layout.buildDirectory.dir(\"generated/javaXmlPatch\")\nProvider<String> javaXmlPatchModuleArg = javaXmlPatchDir.map { directory ->\n    \"--patch-module=java.xml=${directory.asFile.absolutePath}\"\n}\nProvider<String> nativeJavaXmlPatchModuleArg = javaXmlPatchDir.map { directory ->\n